      "author": "LA",
      "description": "## What's New\n\n### New Features\n- **Insert After Text**: Insert links after any specific text in your daily note, not just headings. Links appear in reverse chronological order (newest first).\n- **Exclude Pattern**: Use regex patterns to exclude files from being collected (e.g., `Templates/.*`)\n- **Use Embedded Links**: Toggle whether non-markdown files use `![[file]]` (embedded) or `[[file]]` (regular) links. Defaults to off.\n- **Exclusion Notifications**: Toast notifications now show when files are excluded, with the specific reason (e.g., \"Images disabled\", \"Exclude Pattern\")\n\n### Bug Fixes\n- Fixed `.excalidraw.md` files being collected when \"Only Markdown\" is enabled - they now respect the Excalidraw setting instead\n\n### Issues Closed\n- #2 - Add option to insert after specific heading\n- #4 - Add option to not generate embedded links  \n- #5 - Only collecting Markdown notes still collects Excalidraw files\n- #6 - Allow pattern matching for not linking",
